      "review_text": "Overall enjoyable but perhaps aimed at a more casual puzzle player as there are only a few challenging puzzles amongst many, many simpler puzzles that can be quite obvious. I personally would have preferred fewer, harder puzzles. Some of the solving controls are a bit fiddly for deleting but overall there are good qol features like undo and no timer. (Try the demo if you're not sure as it is is pretty accurate to how the game plays with new rules added as you go. If you like the demo you'll like the full game).",
      "timestamp_created": 1773901983
    },
