      "votes_up": 0,
      "playtime_at_review": 286,
      "review_text": "Didn't realize this was the same developers as Islands of Insight, but I did think it was remarkably similar. Then I saw after closing out of the demo, and bought the game immediately. Great puzzle game, if it's anything like IoI I will likely not finish this game either (which is a good thing, there's tons of puzzles to get stuck on).",
